      Canada's entrepreneur immigration involves government fees, professional services, and settlement costs. The Start-Up Visa is relatively affordable compared to passive investor programs, but budget for legal support and business development costs.
    </p>

    <ComparisonTable columns={costColumns} rows={costRows} />

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-3">Total Cost Estimate (Start-Up Visa)</h3>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Application Costs (Single)</h4>
