        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ Secured CAD $200,000 commitment from angel investor group. Family of 4 approved for PR after 24 months. Relocated to Vancouver. Used Blue Cross family plan during MSP wait (CAD $850/month). Children enrolled in public school. Business now generates CAD $2M annual revenue.</p>
      </div>

