        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">✗ Rejected by all organizations approached—concept not innovative or differentiated enough. Designated orgs receive hundreds of pitches from serious founders with proven traction. Lesson: Start-Up Visa requires genuine innovation and compelling value proposition, not just an idea. Later succeeded after developing product, gaining users, and returning with traction.</p>
      </div>
